The paper deals with the anonymity of transactions in a cryptocurrency, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The analysis involves examining the transactions and identifying patterns, which could also fall under the categories of cybernetics (cs.CY) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves analyzing data, which could fall under the categories of databases (cs.DB) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
